It seems that Mediafire is a untrusty source to upload this piece of art! 

Now on to the introduction! 

Maybe energy drinks give you strength, maybe Okiba's vape settings also give you strength, but the true OG for energy that makes you confident is the power of MUSIC! Now the new and improved inspirational playlist is now into action! Including 
the most popular inspirational songs that can make anything possible, heck, you can even go toe to toe with some random kids Regedit! Including the true og's such as Mortal Kombat theme ,KUNG FU FIGHTIN AND MORE SUCH AS ROCKY'S THEME!

This playlist is useful for killing Clickn 10x faster then usual since he sucks! Also if you are in a desperate situation, such as In  a team fight in which your opponents have better gear and swords, use this and go kamehameha on em! 

What are you waiting for? 
Check the playlist now! https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUDZVeylJrsR8KP_xX_w1z1T9YpH24Uo8

If im sure, only Remember the Name has no profanity and has swear words ;/ Just be cautious lmao
